1959;;The Price of Silence;;British;;Montgomery Tully;;Gordon Jackson, June Thorburn;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Price_of_Silence_(1959_film);;After being released from prison, Roger Fenton (Gordon Jackson) changes his name and starts to build a new life for himself. But his past catches up with him when an elderly visitor is murdered in his office, and his ex-cellmate Slug (Sam Kydd) turns up to blackmail him.